{"tid":807804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新千歲機場取消今日所有航班","createTime":"2018-09-05T23:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T23:55:47.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87cbb5c350ccd617962c965dc4db4cccb54951a5","tid":807804,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:12:52.000Z","msg":"受到6級強震影響，新千歳機場管理公司稍早宣布，國內線、國際線以及航廈將終日封閉，今天一整日由新千歲機場起降的航班全面停飛。<br />\n<br />\n新千歳機場因地震導致停電，航廈出現多處漏水、受理登機櫃台破損，還有牆壁剝落等諸多問題，管理公司宣布一日封閉，進行全面安全檢查。機場關閉後，國土交通省新千歳機場事務所將展開滑走路是否有損害的調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12226/3351440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F12226%2F3351440&d=mE4S28PVtkN9fbRuvdd6pV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8eddee85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/12226/3351440</a>"},{"pid":"3c150b716e795e735402b997f4f8621e72994db3","tid":807804,"uid":200595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757ff4913e4cb05ab898ec53abc86c7ffc2959f5","tid":807804,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"無咗關空，無埋新千歲"},{"pid":"5e19878bdea55e7f91740287aa4782d6a987e5e1","tid":807804,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:20:04.000Z","msg":"港豬無得返鄉下啦陰公"},{"pid":"2cc0258550d53d9141732271bb7ee673f817663e","tid":807804,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"757ff4913e4cb05ab898ec53abc86c7ffc2959f5","tid":807804,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"無咗關空，無埋新千歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"去曬成田羽田"},{"pid":"f1501f353ce1d181f9e80619c76ee922b9763ed0","tid":807804,"uid":53466,"